---
title: Italian Steak & Creamy Pesto Wraps with Chips & Caramelised Onion
description: It's steak and chips, but not how you know it. Fill soft wraps with herbed steak, tomato, crisp cos lettuce, creamy pesto dressing and caramelised onion, and you've got an easy Italian-style dinner that'll go down a treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ebc8400bf84915ded52bc0e-cbae3786.jpg
